---------------------------- title ----------------------------
 How do we check for updates to the Agent?
---------------------------- permalink ----------------------------
how-do-we-check-for-updates-to-the-agent
---------------------------- keywords ----------------------------

---------------------------- body ----------------------------
When the final release is available we’ll have a mechanism for notifying customers about agent updates.

In the meantime, you just need to check back on the plugin drop site to see if there’s been an update.

http://svn.newrelic.com/rpm/agent/newrelic_rpm/version.txt

For information on how to update your agent see:
http://support.newrelic.com/faqs/general-how-tos/installing-the-latest-agent
